Date: 0/0/2004
Source: Notornis
Author:
Vol / Page: 51(4): 193
Edition:
Quote: [Hdg]The tale of the lighthouse-keeper's cat: Discovery and extinction of the Stephens Island wren (<i>Traversia lyalli</i>)... The Stephens Island wren <i>Traversia lyalli</i> is widely quoted as having been discovered and promptly exterminated from its only locality, Stephens Island, New Zealand, by a single lighthouse-keeper's cat. Examination of archival and museum records indicates that this account is  oversimplified...
